      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了。我注意到有两个业务模块：Education_GradeSync和Education_LMS_Portal。它们都是独立的服务吗？还是LMS_Portal是GradeSync内部使用的数据库连接名称？",
      "elements_involved": [
