        "Education_LMS_Portal",
        "mongodb.py"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "Good catch。Education_GradeSync是主服务，mongodb.py是它的生命周期管理模块。Education_LMS_Portal是MongoDB里的具体数据库名称，连接时用的。所以Lifespan节点应该标注为mongodb.py (Education_GradeSync)。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "mongodb.py",
        "Education_GradeSync",
        "Education_LMS_Portal",
        "MongoDB"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "好的，我梳理一下流程：Railway启动容器后调用main.py，main进入lifespan上下文，由mongodb.py负责建立到MongoDB的连接，先connect再ping验证，然后把数据库实例attach回app，最后main配置中间件和路由，向Railway报告服务就绪。这个顺序对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Railway Platform",
        "main.py",
        "lifespan context",
        "mongodb.py",
        "MongoDB",
        "app.mongodb",
        "app.mongo_dal",
