        "router"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对的，关键是那个双向的connection established和pong返回，还有最后attach步骤要显式写出app.mongodb和app.mongo_dal两个属性。服务器监听地址是0.0.0.0:8000。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Connection established",
        "Pong",
        "app.mongodb",
        "app.mongo_dal",
        "0.0.0.0:8000"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已经画好了。四个参与者：Railway Platform、main.py、mongodb.py (Education_GradeSync)、MongoDB。从Start container开始，到Enter lifespan context，然后Connect (Education_LMS_Portal)建立连接，收到Connection established后执行Ping/Pong验证，再Attach两个数据库实例，main自己处理Add CORS middleware和Include router，最后返回Server ready。",
